#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.random.beta.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.random.beta"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.beta.beta:1 of
msgid "Draw samples from a Beta distribution."
msgstr "从 Beta 分布中抽取样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.beta.beta:3 of
msgid ""
"The Beta distribution is a special case of the Dirichlet distribution, "
"and is related to the Gamma distribution.  It has the probability "
"distribution function"
msgstr ""
"Beta 分布是 Dirichlet 分布的特例，并且与 Gamma 分布相关。它具有概率分布"
"函数"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.beta.beta:7 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"f(x; a,b) = \\frac{1}{B(\\alpha, \\beta)} x^{\\alpha - 1}\n"
"(1 - x)^{\\beta - 1},\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.beta.beta:10 of
msgid "where the normalisation, B, is the beta function,"
msgstr "其中归一化常数 B 是 beta 函数，"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.beta.beta:12 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"B(\\alpha, \\beta) = \\int_0^1 t^{\\alpha - 1}\n"
"(1 - t)^{\\beta - 1} dt.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.beta.beta:15 of
msgid "It is often seen in Bayesian inference and order statistics."
msgstr "它常见于贝叶斯推断和顺序统计中。"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.random.beta.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.beta.beta:17 of
msgid "Alpha, non-negative."
msgstr "Alpha，非负。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.beta.beta:19 of
msgid "Beta, non-negative."
msgstr "Beta，非负。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.beta.beta:21 of
msgid ""
"Output shape.  If the given shape is, e.g., ``(m, n, k)``, then ``m * n *"
" k`` samples are drawn.  If size is ``None`` (default), a single value is"
" returned if ``a`` and ``b`` are both scalars. Otherwise, "
"``mt.broadcast(a, b).size`` samples are drawn."
msgstr ""
"输出形状。如果给定的形状是例如 ``(m, n, k)``，则抽取 ``m * n * k`` 个样本"
"。如果 size 是 ``None``（默认），并且 ``a`` 和 ``b`` 都是标量，则返回单个"
"值。否则，抽取 ``mt.broadcast(a, b).size`` 个样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.beta.beta:26 of
msgid "Desired chunk size on each dimension"
msgstr "每个维度上期望的块大小"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.beta.beta:28 of
msgid "Allocate the tensor on GPU if True, False as default"
msgstr "如果为 True 则在 GPU 上分配张量，默认为 False"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.beta.beta:30 of
msgid "Data-type of the returned tensor."
msgstr "返回张量的数据类型。"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.random.beta.rst
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.beta.beta:33 of
msgid "**out** -- Drawn samples from the parameterized beta distribution."
msgstr "**out** -- 从参数化的 beta 分布中抽取的样本。"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.random.beta.rst
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

